    <item>
      <title>因中国需求担忧而暴跌后铁矿石将考验 100 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/iron-ore-set-for-100-test-after-slump-on-china-demand-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铁矿石价格恢复下跌，收于七个月低点，接近每吨 100 美元的水平，这可能会开始推动一些高成本生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/iron-ore-set-for-100-test-after-slump-on-china-demand-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 02:29:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>碧桂园首次未能兑付人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/country-garden-misses-yuan-bond-coupon-payment-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，碧桂园控股有限公司首次未能支付人民币债券的息票，这加剧了这家中国开发商的困境，该开发商目前正面临寻求海外清算的诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/country-garden-misses-yuan-bond-coupon-payment-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 02:09:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>行业报告指出美国库存下降，石油价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于行业报告指出美国原油库存减少，抵消了欧佩克摇摆不定的减产，油价在连续四天下跌后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 23:29:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市涨势停止，日本股市下滑：市场收尾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国股市的涨势稍有喘息，加上丰田工资谈判引发了对日本央行即将加息的押注，亚洲股市举步维艰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 22:27:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
